{"tid":2099882,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"呢間野無牌經營+藍扮黃店","createTime":"2020-07-08T14:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T05:00:35.000Z","uid":54397,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"24c290a50c48b1998c213560114411f835407ba5","tid":2099882,"uid":54397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"珠記冰室 - 呢間野總店係觀塘近碼頭果邊，而家不停係美食廣場開分店。<br />\n<br />\n最近就係將軍澳the parkside包左個美食廣場黎做，但非常可笑的是成個場都未出牌，有食環黎就扮未開始做生意，叫d員工換衫回避。<br />\n<br />\n成個美食廣場有佢地自己珠記冰室、有其他唔同類型既食店，但全部都清一色<span style=\"color: red;\">無牌</span>。<br />\n<br />\n佢地最大既罪名就係藍店扮黃店，勁求其係觀塘總店門口寫幾隻字扮黃，但其實幾個老細都藍到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n點解我會知，因為我細佬係果到做左成年，一蚊人工都無加過，長期番十幾個鐘無補水，係一蚊ot錢都無，咁d ot鐘點計？儲住先，有時比你早走下，放番日假之類咁補，做到我細佬殘到仆街，但連ot錢都無，咁最近我細佬想唔做，老細唔肯放人，仲話你要走隨時可以，但麻煩陪番十四日通知金，我細佬當然火滾，幫你捱到死咁同佢講野。<br />\n<br />\n所以，麻煩大家盡下好市民責任，舉報無牌食肆。<br />\n<br />\n地址：將軍澳唐俊街18號The Parkside 1樓 美食廣場"},{"pid":"ce7e1a08f603892c96f493115013dc6d6c78ea32","tid":2099882,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"借個位唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n{Be water}原來冇咗民陣遊行仲有呢個方法哂民氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2099881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2099881</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ed6cf95d077af5e15ca0c917da6f287f436c2ae7","tid":2099882,"uid":3976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"咁究竟藍在邊到？"},{"pid":"0c61bfba298a62df204f738a6c90e97fd7ffae84","tid":2099882,"uid":54397,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"ed6cf95d077af5e15ca0c917da6f287f436c2ae7","tid":2099882,"uid":3976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"咁究竟藍在邊到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"咁同樣我都唔知佢地黃在邊到"},{"pid":"a4159accec6fb86ac6dd5b6fa565109aa2a81227","tid":2099882,"uid":54397,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"我細佬就係呢間野番緊工，佢本身在觀塘店做最近調左去將軍澳個無牌美食廣場。<br />\n<br />\n個老細日日都屌手足搞到佢地生意跌左幾成，而成個將軍澳班所謂同事只有一個係黃，其他全部藍。"},{"pid":"102aa0998baeac0d2f9b655139f0ff93c1cc65cd","tid":2099882,"uid":280329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"留名等詳細<br />\n但如果照樓主咁講 先唔好分黃藍<br />\n呢間直頭係黑店"},{"pid":"c260d1abb852244d91be0a08008ad42bfac10763","tid":2099882,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:06:12.000Z","msg":"重點 無牌<br />\n推上報"},{"pid":"ff1142fd6504960d82e0e837a139ab0d9798415b","tid":2099882,"uid":17516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"你不如拎d 證據出黎先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92f5b22e6e4968d06fe830202ffb35ac8d38f61","tid":2099882,"uid":54397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ff1142fd6504960d82e0e837a139ab0d9798415b","tid":2099882,"uid":17516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"你不如拎d 證據出黎先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"你想要咩證據？持牌食肆及工廠食堂名單搵唔到佢地餐廳，你唔信大可自己去睇下，至於佢地老細係藍係黃我無必要屈佢，我亦比唔到咩證據你，唔通我叫我細佬同佢吹水果時錄音比你聽？"},{"pid":"bce27ed59581b393df00d7a764eefa49bdc079cb","tid":2099882,"uid":54397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f2813b175e4c1657e24a1fb523e7d1b7ce6c67","tid":2099882,"uid":54397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"大家幫手盡好市民責任，舉報無牌食肆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8840ee20b3e8ad3f8aa4301cc57fea010f534d33","tid":2099882,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"無牌已經報得食環"},{"pid":"7519971860386e13dae22ad30fa62ff7509337c7","tid":2099882,"uid":143151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"點解我會知，因為我細佬係果到做左成年，一蚊人工都無加過，長期番十幾個鐘無補水，係一蚊ot錢都無，咁d ot鐘點計？儲住先，有時比你早走下，放番日假之類咁補，做到我細佬殘到仆街，但連ot錢都無，咁最近我細佬想唔做，老細唔肯放人，仲話你要走隨時可以，但麻煩陪番十四日通知金，我細佬當然火滾，幫你捱到死咁同佢講野<br />\n<br />\n咁有十四日通知咪走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你細佬咁撚天真 你估賣命俾老闆 佢真係會對你好啲咩<br />\n另外啲老闆有幾藍 不如講黎聽下？ 成篇文都睇唔到"},{"pid":"22827dee84440e2f70035bc2dd7ec1b82506ca4b","tid":2099882,"uid":233325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"做黃店真係好L慘，又要被狗搞，又要被對家唱，又要被黃衛兵批鬥。<br />\n啱㗎啦香港人，無遊行，無歌唱，無示威，，連黃色經濟圈都批下批下批散埋，抗爭？<br />\n我覺得啲因為呢一年而入獄同無命嘅手足唔抵，為咗班咁唔團結嘅香港人而犧牲，真係好可惜。"},{"pid":"5a5f422c95054360f3aa3ad59517a29f130edf7a","tid":2099882,"uid":54397,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7519971860386e13dae22ad30fa62ff7509337c7","tid":2099882,"uid":143151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-